Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.46,0:00:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我艾烏巴&扎拉姆聯合
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.11,0:00:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式聲明 參加你們即將發動的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安巴德攻略戰役
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和UE戰鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.89,0:00:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍不作為的話 我們去做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能打下宇宙要塞安巴德
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.13,0:00:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍說不定也會燃起鬥志
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.54,0:00:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你們好運
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢的叛逃者們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始移居殖民衛星後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.59,0:00:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歷經數百年宇宙時代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.29,0:00:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爭奪地球圈霸權的戰爭終於偃旗息鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.17,0:00:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平的時代似乎降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.88,0:00:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 和平卻如此脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.01,0:00:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出現的不明敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令一顆殖民衛星化作宇宙的塵埃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.00,0:00:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這將成為百年漫長戰爭的開端
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.11,0:02:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE系統孕育出的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號的新武器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子爆破加農
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好牛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.53,0:02:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE系統還能設計出這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.97,0:02:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那東西不是你造的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我從沒想過把它用在高達以外的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.19,0:03:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又得和那艘龐大無比的戰艦正面交鋒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.23,0:03:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要想以少勝多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.32,0:03:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必須用強力武器先發制人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先用大招打亂敵人陣腳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後趁亂進攻是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 我們要想獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許只能這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 這些全是古魯迪克的提案
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是那麼蠻幹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於要開始了 與UE的決戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還需要對高達進行調整
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.13,0:03:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號有我們保護
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,XRounder的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果駕御它的話 我還能變得更強吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…能成為救世主嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 尺寸不對？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.60,0:04:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再找一件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 這衣服對女孩子不太體貼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.52,0:04:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我決定了要跟著菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真堅強啊 艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜蕾絲小姐才…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一點也不堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.92,0:04:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是現在也很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼參軍？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.83,0:05:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再 看到更多人傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人害怕不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣能讓更多人安心的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我願意去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直逃避 只會永遠生活在恐懼中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.49,0:05:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特肯定也這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.58,0:05:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才不顧一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.87,0:05:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的菲利特 我決定要永遠跟著他！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份心情 為什麼不讓他知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜…蜜蕾絲小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉好幸福 讓人羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼找不到那樣的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和剛來時判若兩人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.46,0:05:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾夫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等會看你的本事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.98,0:06:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾夫…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾夫 有女朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 當我沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪白的公主小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓她受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為我是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要活著回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊確認機體狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.11,0:06:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20分鐘後作戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉 趁還未進入戰鬥狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不歇會兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.75,0:06:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在艦橋反而讓人安心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎拉姆艦 艾烏巴艦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在向作戰宇域集結
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據報可以在預定時間內完成部署
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 回來以後一起去旅遊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.67,0:07:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會活著回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.12,0:07:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎拉姆艦 艾烏巴艦來電
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦完成作戰準備
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是天神號艦長 古魯迪克·艾諾亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.61,0:07:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同志們 決戰就在眼前了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犧牲不可避免…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須贏得這場戰鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是人類贏取生存權的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是保衛人類尊嚴的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尊嚴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有些古典 但我不討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是為了眾多逝去的生靈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的反擊 從現在開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士隊 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.52,0:07:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉甘·德列斯 Genoace 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GExes 請緊隨其後進入彈射甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾夫 GExes 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也走吧 高達
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特·明日野 高達 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.59,0:08:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 加油 菲利特 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.48,0:08:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士部署完成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:08:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光學傳感器發現安巴德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.25,0:09:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圖像顯示
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.44,0:09:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以放大嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…UE的宇宙要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於讓我找到你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏匿在宇宙中的翼手類！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把敵人給我熏出來
